data.description: Welcome to this charming Victorian home locatted in a prime location close to parks, the train station and downtown Peekskill shops and restaurants- a dream for both contractors and investors alike.  This property boasts great bones and potential with its additional 700 square feet of attic space, offering endless possibilities for expansion or renovation projects.  As you step inside, you're greated by the timeless elegance of hardwood floors that span throughout the main living areas.  The spacious wraparound front porch invites you to unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings, framed by the mature trees dotting the landscape.  While the property presents a blank canvas for your creative vision to flourish.  whether your looking to restore its original charm or embark on a complete transformation, the choice is yours.  Please note the seller will not be making any repairs.  Cash or rehab a loan.  Great opportunity to make this special property your own and unlock its full potential.
